      "text": {
        "format": 1,
        "content": "<p>The <strong>Compendium Index</strong> is an app used to display <a href=\"https://foundryvtt.com/article/compendium/\">compendia</a> for the Shadow of the Weird Wizard system, usually formatted in a way similar to the book's tables.</p><h1>Usage</h1><p>The Compendium Index can only be accessed through <a href=\"https://foundryvtt.wiki/en/development/guides/enrichers\">enricher</a> codes, enabled anywhere where enriched text exists. This includes:</p><ul><li><p><a href=\"https://foundryvtt.com/article/journal/\">Journal entries</a> (like this one!)</p></li><li><p><a href=\"https://foundryvtt.com/article/chat/\">Chat messages</a></p></li><li><p>Fields in <a href=\"https://foundryvtt.com/article/actors/\">actor</a> and <a href=\"https://foundryvtt.com/article/items/\">item</a> sheets where the text editor is used.</p></li><li><p>Other places where a text editor such as this one is used.</p></li></ul><h2>Available Codes</h2><p>Below is the code and result for each existing system compendium.</p><h3>Equipment</h3><table><tbody><tr><td><p><strong>Code</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>Result</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><code>index:‌‌armor</code></p></td><td><p>index:armor</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><code>index:‌‌weapons</code></p></td><td><p>index:weapons</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><code>index:‌‌hirelings</code></p></td><td><p>index:hirelings</p></td></tr></tbody></table><h3>Character Options</h3><table><tbody><tr><td><p><strong>Code</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>Result</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><code>index:‌‌charopts</code></p></td><td><p>index:charopts</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><code>index:‌‌traits</code></p></td><td><p>index:traits</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><code>index:‌‌talents</code></p></td><td><p>index:talents</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><code>index:‌‌spells</code></p></td><td><p>index:spells</p></td></tr></tbody></table>"
      },
